	.col-md-6.adventure-creator-text
		.adventure-creator-header
			Perfect if you...
		.adventure-creator-body
			%ul
				%li Are confident others will join you on a trip
				<br>
				%li	Get uncontrollably excited when planning travel
				<br>
				%li	Are an influencer or can offer unique skills to fellow travelers
				<br>
				%li	Look to maps and forums for off the beaten path trips


